metadata.name: Peek-a-Pepe Open Edition
metadata.description:
Don't miss out on your chance to own a piece of internet history with the limited edition PepeStamp NFT! This open edition will be available for freemint for the next 24 hours only, so act fast and mint your own unique piece of digital art featuring the beloved frog meme.  
Join us and be a part of the ever-growing world of NFTs, and own a one-of-a-kind Pepe stamp that you can treasure forever. Limited quantities available, mint now!
